Part A. Who are Saladin5101
    @Saladin5101 is a man from China. He likes to angrily criticize things he 
  is dissatisfied with and then rewrite them himself (the reason it's not 
  'rewrite a better one' but 'rewrite one' is because sometimes what he re-
  writes is not a better one).
    He is working hard on the E-comOS Operating System Project (EOSP). Altho-
  ugh progress is slow, it can at least start now.
  https://github.com/Saladin5101/.github/blob/main/Screenshot%20From%202026-05-02%2017-47-34.png
    @Saladin5101 also created a language you can use it to wirte code called
  ELFCOST (Easy Language For Computer On Start Time) , see 
  https://github.com/Saladin5101/ecc.git to get more infomations.
  And FNUQ is a new project of @Saladin5101 , it is not host in the 
  GitHub , it is in the https://saladin@git.code.sf.net/p/fnuq/code, you can 
  push your patch to mailing list , more details please see https://sourceforge.net/p/fnuq
Part B. What dose he do and - why his account have so many fork repos.
    First , @Saladin5101 is working for E-comOS Operating System Project 
